data.description: Motivated Sellers, all offers will be considered!! Assumable VA Loan with a fantastic 2.75% Interest Rate!!! Brick home featuring 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths. There are 3 bedrooms on one end of the home with a mother-in-law suite with its own entrance and full bath at the other end! There are original hard wood floors in the dining room, living room, flex space, hallway and 2 bedrooms. The living room has built-in bookcases for books or to display your heirlooms. The flex space can be a 2nd living room or a den and it features French doors leading to the back yard patio. The windows are large with tons of natural light coming in. The back yard is large enough for a pool and a hot tub can be added to the huge patio! Come see this wonderful home only 10 minutes to Tyndall Air Force Base. All measurements are approximate and if important. please have buyers verify.
